hadiths[249]{hadithnumber,text}:
1523,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bhookey ko khana khilao, mareez ki iyaadat karo aur qaidi ko rihai dilao.'' Bukhari ."
1524,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman ke musalman par paanch haq hain : salam ka jawab dena, mareez ki iyaadat karna, janaze ke sath jana, dawat qubul karna aur chheenkne waley ka (yarhamakullah keh kar usey) jawab dena .'' muttafaq aleh."
1525,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalman ke musalman par chhe haq hain.'' arz kya gaya : Allah ke Rasool! wo kya hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab to us se mulaqat karey to usey salam kar, jab wo tumhen dawat dey to usey qubul kar, jab wo tum se nasihat chahey to usey nasihat kar, jab wo chheenk maar kar (alhamdulillah) kahey to to usey (yarhamakullah) keh kar jawab dey, jab bimar ho jaey to uski iyaadat kar aur jab wo faut ho jaey to uskey janaazey ke sath shareek ho.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1526,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen saat chizon ka hukm farmaya aur saat chizon se hamen mana farmaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mareez ki iyaadat kerney, janaazon ke sath shareek honey, chheenk maarney waley ka jawab denay, salam ka jawab denay, dawat deney waley ki dawat qubul kerney, qism uthaney waley ki qism puri karney aur mazlum ki madad karney ka hamen hukm farmaya, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne soney ki anguthi, resham, motey resham, bareek resham, surkh zeen posh, qassi kapdey se aur chaandi ke bartan se hamen mana farmaya, aur eik riwayat mein hai : chaandi ke bartan mein peeney se (mana farmaya) kyonkey jisney is mein duniya mein piya wo aakhirat mein nahin piyega. muttafaq aleh."
1527,"Hazrat Soban Bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab musalman apney musalman bhai ki iyaadat karta hai to wo wapis aaney tak jannat ke mewey khaney mein masroof rehta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1528,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala roze-qiyamat farmaeyga : ibne-Adam! main bimar hua aur tum ne meri iyaadat nahin ki, wo arz kerega : rab ji! main aapki kaisey iyaadat karta jabkey aap to rabbul-aalameen hain. Allah farmaeyga: kya tujhey ilm nahin ke mera falan banda bimar hua tha aur to ne uski iyaadat na ki, agar to uski iyaadat karta to mujhey uskey paas paata, ibne-Adam! maine tum se khana talab kya lekin tu ney mujhey khana na diya, wo arz kerega : rab ji! main tumhen kaisey deta, jabkey to rabbul-aalamin hai, Allah farmaeyga : kya tujhey ilm nahin ke merey falan bandey ne tujh se khana talab kya tha lekin tu ney isey khana nahin khilaya, kya tujhey ilm nahin ke agar to usey khana khilata to us (ke sawab ( ko merey paas paata, ibne-Adam! maine tujh se pani talab kya tha lekin tu ney mujhey pani nahin pilaya , wo arz kerega rab ji ! main tujhey kaisey pani pilata jabkey to tamam jahano ka rab hai, Allah farmaeyga : merey falan bandey ne tujh se pani talab kya tha lekin tu ney isey pani na pilaya , agar to usey pani pilata to to us (ke sawab ( ko merey paas paata .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1529,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik eraab (dehati shakhs) ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley gaey, jab aap kisi mareez ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley jatey to yun farmatey : '' koi baat nahin, agar Allah ne chaha to ( ye bimari gunahon sey) pakizgi ka baais hogi .'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bhi yehi farmaya : ''koi baat nahin, agar Allah ne chaha, to ( ye bimari gunahon sey) pakizgi ka baais hogi .'' us eraab ne kaha : hergiz nahin, balke bukhar eik boodhey shakhs par josh maar raha hai, ye to qabron tak pahuncha kar rahega. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (us ki ye baat sun kar) farmaya : '' haan ! ye aisey hi hoga .'' Bukhari."
1530,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab ham mein se koi bimar ho jata to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is par apna daayan haath phertey phir ye dua padhtey : '' logon ke parwardigar ! bimari door kar dey , shifa ata farma , terey siwa koi shifa deney wala nahin, to shifa deney wala hai, aur aisi shifa ata farma jo kisi bimari ko baqi na chodey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1531,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab insan ke kisi uzu ko koi takleef hoti ya usey koi phoda hota ya koi zakhm hota to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni ungli se ishara kartey huey farmatey : ''Allah ke naam (ki barkat) sey, hamari zamin ki mitti, hamarey baaz ki thook ke sath Allah ke hukm se hamarey bimar ko shifa bakhshi jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1532,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar hotey to aap muawwizat padh kar apney aap par dam kartey aur apney jism par apna haath phertey, jab aap marzul-maut mein mubtala huey to phir main aap ko muawwizaat padh kar dam kya karti thi jo ke aap apney aap ko dam kya kartey they lekin main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath aap ke jism par pherti thi. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, farmati hain : jab aap ke ehle khana mein se koi shakhs mareez hota to aap muawwizaat padh kar is par dam kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1533,"Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney apney jism ki takleef ke mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shikayat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''apney jism ki takleef waley hissey par apna haath rakho, aur teen martaba bismillah padh kar saat martaba ye dua padho : اعوذ بعزۃ اللہ و قدرتہ من شر ما اجد و احاذرmain her us shar se jo main paata hun aur jis se main gham zada hun Allah ke ghalbey aur uski qudrat ki panah chahta hun.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine aisey kya to Allah ne meri wo takleef door kar di. rawahu Muslim."
1534,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Jibrael (Alaihissalam) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney farmaya : Muhammad ! aap bimar hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan ! '' to unhoney yun dam kya : main aap ko takleef deney wali her chiz sey, her nafs ke shar se ya haasid ki nazar se Allah ke naam ke sath aap ko dam karta hun, Allah aap ko shifa ata farmaey, main Allah ke naam ke sath aapko dam karta hun. rawahu Muslim."
1535,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hasan w Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko un kalimaat ke sath Allah ki panah mein detey they : ''main Allah ke kalimaate-taamma ke zariey her shetan, zahreeley janwer aur her nuqsan pahunchanewali nazar ke shar se tumhen bachata hun.'' aur aap farmaya kartey they : '' tumharey baap ( Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ( un kalimaat ke zariey Ismail (Alaihissalam) w Is-haq (Alaihissalam) ke liye panah talab kya kartey they.'' Bukhari, masaabeh ke aksar nuskhon mein tasniya ka seegha [ بھما ] hai. rawahu Muslim ."
1536,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah jiskey sath bhalai ka irada karta hai to usey kisi musibat mein mubtala kar deta hai.'' Bukhari ."
1537,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman ko jo pareshani, gham, ranj, takleef aur dukh pahunchta hai yahan tak ke agar usey koi kaanta bhi chubhta hai to Allah us ( takleef ( ki wajeh se uskey gunah maaf farma deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1538,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap bukhar mein mubtala they, maine aapko apna haath lagaya to maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! aap to bahut sakht bukhar mein mubtala hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, mujhey tumharey do aadmiyon jaisa bukhar hota hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : maine arz kya, ye isliye ke aap ke liye do guna ajr hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan ! '' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab musalman ko kisi marz ya kisi aur wajeh se koi takleef pahunchti hai to Allah us wajeh se uskey gunah is tarah gira deta hai jis tarah (patjhad mausam mein) darkht apney pattey gira deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1539,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada kisi ko takleef mein mubtala nahin dekha. muttafaq aleh."
1540,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai to aap ka sar Mubarak meri thodi aur seeney ke darmiyan tha, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ki maut ki sakhti) ke baad mein kisi par maut ki sakhti ko kabhi bura nahin samajhti. Bukhari."
1541,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin ki misal kheti ki naram w naazuk shaakh ki tarah hai jisey hawayen jhukaati hain. kabhi usey nichey gira deti hain aur kabhi sidha kar deti hain, yahan tak ke uski ajal aa jati hai, jabkey munafiq ki misal sanubar ke darkht ki tarah hai, jis par koi chiz asar-andaz nahin hoti yahan tak ke wo eik hi martaba toot jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1542,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin ki misal kheti ki si hai jisey hua jhuka deti hai, aur momin ko masaayib aatey rehtey hain, jabkey munafiq ki misal sanubar ke darkht ki tarah hai wo harkat nahin karta yahan tak ke usey kaat diya jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1543,"Hazrat Jabir bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Umme-Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif ley gaey to farmaya : ''aap kyon kaanp rahi hain?'' unhoney bataya : bukhar hai, Allah usey barkat na dey . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bukhar ko bura bhala na kaho , kyonkey wo bani-Adam ke gunahon ko is tarah khatam kar deta hai jis tarah bhatti lohey ki mail kuchail door kar deti hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1544,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda bimar ho jaey ya wo safar par ho to uskey liye itna hi amal (sawab) likh diya jata hai jitna wo haalate-qiyam aur haalat sehat mein kya karta tha.'' Bukhari ."
1545,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''taaun musalman ki shahadat hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1546,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shaheed paanch qism ke hain, taaun ke marz sey, pet ke marz sey, doob janey se faut honey wala, kisi deewar waghera ke nichey dab kar mar janey wala aur Allah ki raah mein Shahid ho janey wala.'' muttafaq aleh."
1547,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se taaun ke barey mein puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo to eik tarah ka azab hai, Allah jis par chahta hai usey musallat kar deta hai, aur Allah ne usey mominon ke liye rehmat banaya hai, jo shakhs taaun ki waba aa janey par sabr aur sawab ki ummid kartey huey aur ye jantey huey ke Allah ne jo uskey mutalliq likh diya hai wo usey pahunch kar rahega, apney shehar mein thehar jata hai to uskey liye Shahid ke misl ajr w sawab hai.'' Bukhari ."
1548,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''taaun eik tarah ka azab hai jo bani-Israel ke eik giroh par ya tum se pehley logon par bheja gaya tha, jab tum kisi mulk mein uskey phel janey ke mutalliq suno to tum us mulk ki taraf pesh qadmi na karo aur jab kisi sar zamin par phel jaey aur tum wahan mojud ho to phir wahan se raah farar ikhtiyar na karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
1549,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah subhanahu w taala ne farmaya : jab main apney bandey ko uski do chizon yani dono aakhon se mehrum karkey aazmata hun aur wo is par sabr karta hai to main unke iwaz usey jannat ata karta hun.'' Bukhari ."
1550,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo musalman kisi musalman ki subh ke waqt iyaadat karta hai to Sham honey tak sattar hazar farishtey is par rahmatein bhejtey rehtey hain aur agar wo Sham ke waqt uski iyaadat karta hai to subh honey tak sattar hazar farishtey uskey liye dua kartey rehtey hain aur uskey liye jannat main eik baagh tayyar kar diya jata hai.''"
1551,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, meri aakhon mein takleef thi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne meri iyaadat farmaai. rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ."
1552,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs achi tarah wuzu karkey sawab ki niyat se apney musalman bhai ki iyaadat karta hai to usey saath saal ki masafat ke barabar jahannam se door kar diya jata hai.''"
1553,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman kisi musalman ki iyaadat ke waqt saat martaba ye dua padhey : main Allah Azeem, rab arshe-azeem se darkhast karta hun ke wo tumhen shifa ata farmaey, to Allah Taala usey shifa ata farma deta hai b-sharte-ke ke uski maut ka waqt na aa chuka ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
1554,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bukhar aur her qism ki takleef ke mutalliq unhen ye dua sikhaya kartey they : ''Allah kabir ke naam ke sath mein her josh maarney wali rag ke shar aur aag ki haraarat ke shar se Allah azeem ki panah chahta hun.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai ye sirf Ibrahim bin-Ismail ki sanad se maroof hai jabkey usey hadees mein zaeef qarar diya gaya hai."
1555,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''tum mein se kisi shakhs ko koi takleef pahunchey ya uskey bhai ko koi takleef pahunchey to wo yun dua karey to wo theek ho jaeyga : hamara rab Allah hai jo ke aasmano mein hai, tera naam paak hai, zamin w aasman par tera Amr aisey hi hai jaisey teri rehmat aasman mein hai, pas zamin par bhi apni rehmat farma, hamarey kabira gunah aur khataeyn maaf farma, to (gunahon sey) paak logon ka rab hai, apni rehmat se rehmat nazil farma, aur us takleef par apni shifa se shifa nazil farma."
1556,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi kisi mariz ki iyaadat ke liye aaye to yun dua karey : aey Allah! apney bandey ko shifa ata farma, wo teri raza ki khatir dushman se jihad kerega ya teri raza ki khatir janaazey ke liye jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1557,"Hazrat Ali bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Umayya se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Allah azz-w-jall ke us farman : ''chaahey tum dil ki baaton ko zahir karo ya poshida rakho, Allah tum se zarur uska muhaasba kerega.'' neez ''aur jo koi bura kaam kerega to uska usey badla diya jaeyga.'' ke mutalliq Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha to unhoney farmaya : jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha uskey mutalliq mujh se kisi ne daryaft nahin kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bandey ko bukhar aur musibat waghera aati hai to ye Allah ki taraf se pakad hai yahan tak ke agar wo apni qameez ki jeib mein kuch raqam rakh kar usey gum kar bethta hai aur is par wo pareshan hota hai (to ye bhi uskey gunahon ka kaffara bin jata hai) yahan tak ke banda apney gunahon se is tarah saaf ho jata hai jis tarah surkh sona bhatti se saaf ho kar nikalta hai.''"
1558,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bandey ko chhoti-badi musibat pahunchti hai to wo uskey gunahon ki wajeh se pahunchti hai, aur jin se Allah Taala darguzar farmata hai wo to kahin ziyada hain.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''aur tumhen jo musibat pahunchti hai wo tumharey apney hi aamaal ka nateeja hoti hai aur wo aksar buraiyan maaf kar deta hai.''"
1559,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda achey andaz mein ibadat karta hai aur phir wo bimar ho jata hai to is par muqarrar kiye huey farishtey se kaha jata hai : uskey amal wesay hi likhtey jaao jaisey ye haalate-sehat mein amal kya karta tha yahan tak ke main usey sehatyaab kar dun ya usey apney paas bula lun.'' (rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah) ."
1560,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab musalman kisi jismani aazmaaish se do-chaar ho jata hai to farishtey se keh diya jata hai : uskey wo Saleh amal likhtey chaley jaao jo wo pehley haalate-sehat mein kya karta tha, agar wo usey shifa bakhsh dey to wo usey gunahon se paak saaf kar deta hai, aur agar uski rooh qabz kar ley to wo usey maaf farma deta hai aur wo is par rehmat farmata hai.'' (rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
1561,"Hazrat Jabir bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein Shahid honey ke ilawa shahadat ki saat qismen hain : taaun ke marz sey, doob janey sey, nimoniye ke marz sey, pet ke marz sey, jal kar wafat pane-waley aur kisi bojh taley dab kar marney waley Shaheed hain aur bachey ki paidaish par faut ho janey wali aurat bhi Shaheed hai. rawahu Malik w Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
1562,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya kin logon par sab se ziyada masaayib aatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) phir jo unke baad afzal hain, phir jo unke baad afzal hain, aadmi ko uskey Deen ke hisab hi se aazmaya jata hai, agar to wo apney Deen mein pukhta ho to uski aazmaaish bhi sakht hoti hai. aur agar wo Deen mein naram aur kamzor ho to uski aazmaish bhi Sehal hoti hai, ye maamla isi tarah chalta rehta hai yahan tak ke wo satahe-zameen par is tarah chalta hai ke uskey zimmey koi gunah nahin hota.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Darmi, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1563,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki maut ki sakhti dekhney ke baad kisi ke aasan marney par mein rashk nahin kya karti. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai."
1564,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko nazaa (jism se jan nikalney) ke aalim mein dekha, aap ke paas pani ka eik piyala tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna haath piyaley mein daltey, phir apney chehrey par haath phertey aur farmatey : ''aey Allah! maut ki naagawaariyon aur maut ki be hoshiyon par meri madad farma.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
1565,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah Taala apney bandon se khair w bhalai ka irada farmata hai to usey uskey gunahon ki saza duniya hi mein dey deta hai, aur jab apney bandey se shar ka irada farmata hai to uskey gunah ke mamley ko muakhkhar farma deta hai yahan tak ke wo uskey badley mein roze-qiyamat usey pura pura badla dega.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1566,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak badi jaza badi aazmaaish ke sath hai, kyonkey Allah azz-w-jall jab kisi qom se mohabbat karta hai to wo unhen aazmata hai, jo shakhs is par razi ho to usey razamandi hasil ho jati hai, aur jo shakhs narazi ka izhar karey to wo uski narazi ka mustahiq theharta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
1567,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin par uski jaan w maal aur uski aulad ke barey mein aazmaaish aati rehti hai yahan tak ke wo Allah Taala se mulaqat karta hai to uskey zimmey koi khata nahin hoti.'' Tirmizi, Imam Malik ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1568,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Khalid Salma apney walid se aur wo uskey dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak bandey ke liye Allah ke yahan koi maqam w martaba muqaddar hota hai jahan wo apney amal ke zariey nahin pahunch sakta to Allah usey uskey jism ya uskey maal ya uski aulad ke barey mein aazmata hai, phir usko is par sabr karney ki tofiq ata farmata hai yahan tak ke wo usey us maqam w martabe tak pahuncha deta hai jo Allah ki taraf se uskey liye muqaddar kya hota hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood."
1569,"Hazrat Abdullah bin shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ibne-Adam ko is haal mein takhleeq kya jata hai ke uskey pehlu mein ninnanwey mohlik balaeyn hoti hain, agar wo unse bach bhi jata hai to wo budhapey mein mubtala ho jata hai, yahan tak ke wo faut ho jata hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1570,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aazmaaish se do-chaar logon ko roze-qiyamat jaza di jaeygi to ehle-aafiyat khaahish karengey ke kaash! duniya mein unki jildon ko qenchiyon se kaat diya jata.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1571,"Hazrat Aamir raam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne beemariyon (aur unke sawab (ka zikr kya to farmaya : ''jab momin ko koi bimari laahiq hoti hai aur phir Allah azz-w-jall usey us se aafiyat w sehat ata farma deta hai to wo ( marz ( uskey pichhley gunahon ka kaffara aur mustaqbil ke barey mein waaz w nasihat bin jati hai, aur jab munafiq bimar hota hai phir usey aafiyat ata kar di jati hai to wo us oont ki tarah hota hai jisey uskey ghar walon ne baandh rakha ho aur phir unhoney usey chhod diya ho usey pata nahin hota ke unhoney usey kyon baandha tha aur kyon chhoda hai.'' kisi shakhs ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! beemariyan kya hoti hain? Allah ki qism ! main to kabhi bimar nahin hua , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hamarey paas se chaley jaao , tum ham mein se nahin ho.''"
1572,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mareez ke paas jaao to uski lambi umr ki baat karo bila-shuba ye taqdir to nahin badal sakta lekin uska dil khush ho jaeyga.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1573,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Sarad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko uska pet ( pet ki koi bimari ( halak kar dey , usey qabr mein azab nahin diya jaeyga.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
1574,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Yahudi ladka Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kya karta tha, wo bimar ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey sarhaney beth kar usey farmaya : '' musalman ho ja .'' usney apney paas bethey huey apney walid ki taraf dekha to usney kaha : abul-Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat maan ley, pas wo musalman ho gaya, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye farmatey huey wahan se tashrif laye : '' her qism ki hamd w tareef aur shukr Allah ke liye hai jisney usko jahannam se bacha liya .'' Bukhari ."
1575,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs mareez ki iyaadat karta hai to aasman se aawaz deney wala aelan karta hai : aap achey rahey aur aap ka chalna bhi achcha raha aur aapney jannat main eik ghar bana liya .''"
1576,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke maut ke marz mein aap ke paas se bahar tashrif laye to Sahaba ne puchha : abul-Hasan ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ab kaisey hain? unhoney kaha : alhamdulillah, behtar hain. Bukhari ."
1577,"Hazrat Ata bin abi Ribah bayan kartey hain, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey farmaya : ''kya main tumhen khatoone-jannat na dikhaaun? maine kaha : kyon nahin, zarur dikhayen , unhoney farmaya : ye siyah faam khatoon , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey mirgi ka daurah padta hai to mera sattar khul jata hai. aap Allah se dua farmaeyn. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to chahey to sabr kar aur terey liye jannat hai aur agar to chahey to main Allah se dua karta hun ke wo tumhen sehat ata farmaey.'' us khatoon ne arz kya, main sabr karungi, phir usney arz kya : kyonkey mera sattar khul jata hai, lihaza aap Allah se dua farmaain ke mera sattar na khula karey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey liye dua farmaey. muttafaq aleh."
1578,"Hazrat Yahya bin Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke kisi aadmi ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein maut aai to kisi aadmi ne kaha, uski khush-naseebi hai ke wo kisi marz mein mubtala huey baghair faut ho gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujh par afsos! tumhen kya maloom? ke agar Allah usey kisi marz mein mubtala karta to wo uskey gunah mita deta.'' Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey mursal riwayat kya hai."
1579,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) aur Sunabihi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo kisi mareez ki iyaadat ke liye gaey to unhoney us se kaha : tumhara kya haal hai? usney kaha : mujh par nemat w Fazal hai, is par Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : gunahon aur khataon ke maaf ho janey par khush ho jaao, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak Allah azz-w-jall farmata hai : jab main apney kisi momin bandey ko aazmata hun to wo merey us aazmaney par meri hamd aur shukr baja lata hai to wo apney us bistar se us roz ki tarah gunahon se paak saaf uthta hai jis roz uski walida ne usey janm diya tha, aur rab tabarak w taala farmata hai : maine apney bandey ko rokey rakha aur usey aazmaaish mein dala, tum usey wesay hi ajr ata kar do jis tarah tum usey uskey sehat mand honey ki surat mein ajr diya kartey they.'' rawahu Ahmed."
1580,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab bandey ke gunah bahut ziyada ho jatey hain aur uska aisa koi amal nahin hota jo un gunahon ka kaffara bin jaey to Allah usey huzn w gham mein mubtala kar deta hai taake wo uskey gunahon ka kaffara bin jaey.''"
1581,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi mareez ki iyadat karta hai to wo rehmat mein dakhil hota chala jata hai. yahan tak ke wo (uskey paas) beth jata hai, pas jab wo beth jata hai to wo us (rehmat) mein ghota zan ho jata hai.''"
1582,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko bukhar ho jaey, kyonkey bukhar aag ka eik tukda hai. to usey pani ke zariey thanda karey, wo kisi nehare-rawan mein dakhil ho jaey aur jidhar se pani aa raha hai us taraf munh karey, aur ye dua padhey : Allah ke naam ke sath, aey Allah! apney bandey ko shifa ata farma, aur apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tasdeeq farma, aur ye amal tulue-subh ke baad se tulu aaftaab se pehley pehley karey, aur teen din is mein teen ghotey lagaey, agar teen din mein theek na ho to paanch din, agar paanch din mein theek na ho to phir saat din aur agar saat din mein theek na ho to phir no din, aur Allah azz-w-jall ke hukm se no din se ziyada nahin hoga.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1583,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bukhar ka zikr kya gaya to kisi aadmi ne usey bura-bhala kaha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey bura bhala na kaho , kyonkey wo gunahon ko aisey saaf kar deta hai jaisey aag lohey ki mail kuchail door kar deti hai.'' , ( rawahu ibne-Maja ( ."
1584,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi mareez ki iyaadat ki to farmaya : '' khush ho jaao , kyonkey Allah Taala farmata hai, wo (bukhar) meri aag hai main usey duniya mein apney momin bandey par musallat karta hun taake wo uskey liye roze-qiyamat ki aag ke hisse ka (badla) ho jaey.'' (rawahu Ahmed w ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Eman)."
1585,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''rab Subhanahu w taala farmata hai : mujhey merey ghalba w jalal ki qasam! main jisey bakhshney ka irada kar lun to main usey duniya se nahin uthata yahan tak ke main usey bimar karkey ya uskey rizq mein tangi karkey uskey zimmey tamam khataaon ka pura-pura hisab na kar lun.'' ( لااصل لہ ( rawahu rizeen.
1586,"Hazrat Shaqiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey to ham unki iyaadat ke liye gaey to wo roney lagey, pas is par unko malamat kya gaya, to unhoney farmaya : main marz ki wajeh se nahin rota, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' marz ( gunahon ka ( kaffara hota hai.'' main to isliye rota hun ke ye ( marz ( mujhey budhapey ki umr mein laahiq hua hai, aur mehnat w mashaqqat karney ke daur mein laahiq nahin hua, kyonkey jab aadmi bimar ho jata hai to uskey liye wohi ajr likh diya jata hai jo uskey bimar honey se pehley likha jata tha, aur ab sirf marz ne usey (wo aamaal baja laney sey) rok rakha hai. ( لااصل لہ ( rawahu rizeen."
1587,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen din ke baad iyaadat ke liye jaya kartey they."
1588,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mareez ke paas jaao to usey kaho ke wo tumharey haq mein dua karey, kyonkey uski dua, farishton jaisi hai.''"
1589,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mareez ki iyaadat kartey waqt uskey paas mukhtasar waqt ke liye bethna aur shor kam karna sunnat hai. unhoney bayan kya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas unka shor aur ikhtilaf ziyada hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas se chaley jaao.'' ( لااصل لہ ( rawahu rizeen."
1590,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''iyaadat (itney waqt ke liye kerni chahiye) jitna waqt doodh ki do dhaarein nikalney ke darmiyan hota hai.''"
1591,aur Saeed bin musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) ki mursal riwayat mein hai : ''behtareen iyaadat wo jis mein (iyaadat karkey) jaldi utha jaey.''
1592,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi aadmi ki iyaadat ki to farmaya : ''kisi chiz ko dil chahta hai?'' usney arz kya : gehun ki roti, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke paas gehun ki roti ho to wo usey apney bhai ke paas bhej dey.'' phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumharey kisi mareez ka kisi chiz ko dil chahey to wo usey khila diya karo.''"
1593,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Madina mein paida honey wala eik shakhs faut ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski Namaze-janaza padh kar farmaya : ''kash ke ye apni jaey-paidaish ke ilawa kisi aur jagah faut hota.'' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! kis liye? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak jab koi aadmi apni jaey paidaish ke ilawa kisi jagah faut hota hai to uski jaey paidaish se jaey wafat tak ke fasley ke barabar usey jannat ata kar di jati hai.'' rawahu Nasai w ibne-Maja."
1594,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pardes ki maut shahadat hai.''"
1595,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bimari ki haalat mein faut hota hai to wo shahadat ki maut marta hai, usey qabr ke fitney se bacha liya jata hai, subh w Sham usey jannat se rizq pahuncha diya jata hai.''"
1596,"Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shuda aur apney bistaron par wafat paney waley, taaun ki wajeh se faut honey walon ke barey mein hamarey rab azz-w-jall ke samney muqadma pesh karengey to shuda arz karengey : hamarey bhai hain wo wesay hi Shahid kiye gaey jaisey ham Shahid kiye gaey, jabkey faut honey waley kahengey, ye hamarey bhai hain, ye bhi wesay hi apney bistaron par faut huey jis tarah ham faut huye, hamara rab farmaeyga : unke zakhm dekho, agar to unke zakhm, maqtooleen (shuda) ke zakhmon ki tarah hain to phir ye un mein se hain aur unke sath hain, pas unke zakhm unhi ke zakhmon se mushabeh they.'' rawahu Ahmed w Nasai."
1597,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' taaoon se farar honey wala maidane-jihad se farar honey waley ki tarah hai, aur wahan sabr karney (ruk janey) waley ke liye Shaheed ka sawab hai.''"
1598,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi maut ki tamanna na karey, agar to wo neku-kaar hai to shayad ke wo nekiyon mein izafa kar ley, aur agar wo khata kaar hai to shayad ke wo tauba kar ley.'' Bukhari ."
1599,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi maut ki tamanna karey na uskey aaney se pehley uskey liye dua karey, kyonkey jab wo faut ho jata hai to uski ummid munqata ho jati hai, aur momin ki umr to uskey liye khair w bhalai ke izafe ka baais hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1600,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs kisi takleef pahunchney par maut ki tamanna na karey, agar usko zarur kehna hai to wo yun kahey : aey Allah! jab tak mera zinda rehna merey liye behtar hai tab tak mujhey zinda rakhna, aur jab wafat merey liye behtar ho tab mujhey ( duniya sey) utha lena.'' muttafaq aleh."
1601,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat karna pasand karta hai to Allah uski mulaqat ko pasand karta hai.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ya aap ki kisi aur zauja mohtarma ne farmaya : be-shak ham to maut ko na pasand kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye baat nahin hai, balke momin ko maut aati hai to usey Allah ki razamandi aur uski izzat afzaai ki khushkhabri di jati hai to phir jo uskey aagey honey wala hota hai wo usey sab se ziyada mehbub hota hai lihaza wo Allah se mulaqat karna pasand karta hai aur Allah us se mulaqat karna pasand karta hai, aur jab kafir ko maut aati hai to usey Allah ke azab aur uski saza ki basharat di jati hai to phir usko mustaqbil se ziyada nagawar koi chiz nazar nahin aati to wo Allah se mulaqat karna napasand karta hai aur Allah us se milna napasand karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1602,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai : ''Allah ki mulaqat se pehley maut hai.'' rawahu Muslim .
1603,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) hadees bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se eik janaza guzra to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye rahat pa gaya ya doosrey us se rahat pa gaey.'' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! ye rahat pa gaya ya doosrey us se rahat pa gaey us se kya murad hai? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bandae-momin duniya ki mushkilat aur takleefon se rahat pa kar Allah ki rehmat ki taraf jata hai jabkey faajir shakhs se log aur duniya aur darkht w haiwaanat rahat pa jatey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1604,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey kandhey se pakad kar farmaya : ''duniya mein kisi ajnabi shakhs ya kisi raah-guzar ki tarah raho.'' aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : jab Sham ho jaey to subh ka intizar na karo, aur jab subh ho jaey to phir Sham ka intizar na karo, aur sehat main apni bimari ke liye aur apni hayaat se apni maut ke liye tosha hasil karo. Bukhari ."
1605,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aapki wafat se teen roz qabl, farmatey huey suna : ''tumhen Allah se husne-zan ki surat mein maut aani chahiye.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1606,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum chaho to main tumhen bataey deta hun ke roze-qiyamat sab se pehley Allah mominon se kya farmaeyga aur wo sab se pehley us se kya arz karengey ?'' ham ne arz kya ji haan Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''Allah mominon se farmaeyga : kya tum mujhey milna pasand kartey they? wo arz karengey : ji haan , hamarey parwardigar ! wo puchega : kis liye? wo arz karengey : hamen aap ki maafi w darguzar aur maghfirat ki ummid thi, wo farmaeyga pas meri maghfirat tumharey liye wajib ho gaee.''"
1607,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''lazzaton ko kaat deney wali, maut ko kasrat se yad kya karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja."
1608,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz apney Sahaba se farmaya : ''Allah se haya karo jis tarah us se haya karney ka haq hai.'' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke nabi! alhamdulillah ham Allah se haya kartey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye baat nahin hai, balke jo shakhs Allah se aisey haya karta hai jaisey haya karney ka haq hai to wo sar aur un chizon ki jo sar mein hain (aankh, kaan, zaban) ki hifazat karey, aur wo pet aur uskey mutaalliqaat (sharm-gah, haath, paaon aur dil waghera) ki hifazat karey, wo maut aur boseedah honey ko yad rakhey, aur jo aakhirat chahta hai wo duniya tarak kar dey. jo shakhs is tarah karey to usney Allah se aisey haya ki jaisey us se haya karney ka haq hai.''"
1609,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' maut momin ke liye tohfa hai.''"
1610,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin marta hai to uski peshani par pasina aa jata hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
1611,"Hazrat Ubaidullah bin Khalid bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achanak maut, ghazab ki giraft hai.'' Abu-Dawood . Imam Behaqi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Shobil-emaan mein aur rizeen ne apni kitab mein ye izafa naqal kya hai : ''ghazab ki pakad kafir ke liye hai jabkey momin ke liye rehmat hai.''"
1612,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik nojawan shakhs ke paas gaey jabkey wo nazaa (jism se jaan nikalney) ki haalat mein tha, aapney farmaya : ''tum kaisa mehsus kartey ho ?'' usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main Allah se ummid rakhta hun aur apney gunahon se darta hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aisey moqe par kisi bandey ke dil mein do chizen ( ummid aur khof ( ikhatti ho jaeyn to Allah usey wo chiz ata farma deta hai jiski wo ummid karta hai aur jis chiz se wo dar raha hota hai us se usey be khof kar deta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
1613,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maut ki tamanna na karo, kyonkey marney ke baad ke samaan ki holnaaki bahut sakht hai, aur ye saadat ki baat hai ke bandey ki umr daraz ho jaey aur Allah azz-w-jall usey apni taraf ruju karney ki tofiq ata farmaey.'' rawahu Ahmed."
1614,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf tawajjoh karkey bethey huey they, aapney hamen waaz w nasihat ki aur hamarey dilon ko naram kya to Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) roney lagey, unhoney bahut ziyada rotey huey keh diya : kaash! ke main mar jata, ye sun kar, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Saad! kya tum merey hotey huey maut ki tamanna kartey ho?'' aapney ye baat teen martaba dohraai, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Saad! agar tumhen jannat ke liye paida kya gaya hai to phir tumhari umr jitni daraz hogi aur tumharey jitney amal achey hongey wo tumharey liye behtar hai.''"
1615,"Hazrat Harisa bin Muzrib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Khabbab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya to unhoney jism ko saat jagahon par daagha hua tha, unhoney kaha : agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey na suna hota : ''tum mein se koi maut ki tamanna na karey.'' to main zarur uski tamanna karta maine apney aap ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath is tarah bhi dekha hai ke merey paas eik dirham bhi nahin tha, jabkey ab merey ghar ke eik koney mein chaalis hazar dirham hain. Harisa bayan kartey hain, phir unka kafan laya gaya, jab unhoney usey dekha to roney lagey aur farmaya : '' lekin Hamza ko kafan ke liye eik chhoti si dhaari daar chadar nasib hui, jab usey unke sar par kya jata to paaon se ikhatti ho jati aur jab paaon par ki jati to sar ki taraf se ikhatti ho jati , yahan tak ke usey unke sar par phela diya gaya aur unke paaon par ghaas dal di gaee .'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, albatta Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye zikr nahin kya ke phir unke liye kafan laya gaya, aakhir hadees tak . rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
1616,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney qaribul-maut afrad ko (la Ilaah illallah) ki talqin karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1617,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum kisi mareez ya maiyat ke paas jaao to achi baat kaho , kyonkey tum jo baat kartey ho to farishtey is par Aameen kehtey hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1618,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman kisi musibat ke aaney par Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq ye dua padhta hai : be-shak ham Allah ki milkiyat hain aur ham usi ki taraf lot kar janey waley hain, aey Allah ! meri is musibat par mujhey ajr w sawab ata farma aur mujhey us se behtar badal ata farma . to Allah usey us se behtar badal ata farma deta hai.'' pas jab abu Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey to maine kaha : abu Salma se behtar kon musalman shakhs hoga, ye wo pehla gharaana hai jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf hijrat ki thi, phir main wo dua padhti rahi to Allah ne mujhey badley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ata farma diye. rawahu Muslim ."
1619,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif laye to unki nazar phat chuki thi, aapney unki aankhen band kin phir farmaya : ''jab rooh qabz ki jati hai to nazar uskey peechey chali jati hai.'' ( ye sun kar) unke ehle-khana roney lagey, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney liye dua khair hi karo, kyonkey tum jo kehtey ho, farishtey is par Aameen kehtey hain.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! abu-Salma ki maghfirat farma, hidayat yafta logon mein uska darja buland farma, uskey peechey baqi reh janey walon main to uska Khalifa bin ja, tamam jahano ke parwardigar! hamen aur usey bakhsh dey, uski qabr ko kushada farma aur usey munawwar farma.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1620,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai to aap ko dhaari daar suti chadar se dhanp diya gaya. muttafaq aleh."
1621,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ka aakhiri kalam (''la Ilaah illallah'') hoga wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' ( rawahu Abu-Dawood ( ."
1622,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney qaribul-marg afrad par Sura Ya-Seen padhi. ki tilawat karo.''"
1623,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) wafat pa gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rotey huey unka bosa liya yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aansu Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke chehrey par gir padey.
1624,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wafat pa gaey to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unka bosa liya. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja.
1625,"Hazrat Husain bin Wahwah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Talha bin Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mera khayal hai ke Talha faut honey wala hai, pas uski mujhey ittilaa karna aur) dafn karney mein) jaldi karna , kyonkey musalman maiyat ko uskey ehle khana ke paas rok rakhna munasib nahin .''"
1626,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney qaribul-marg (maut ke qareeb) afrad ko in kalimaat ki talqin karo : Haleem aur karim Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, Allah arshe-azeem ka Rab paak hai, her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jo tamam jahano ka parwardigar hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! (ye kalimaat) zindon ke mutalliq kaisey hain? aapney farmaya : bahut khub ! bahut khoob.''"
1627,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qaribul-marg (maut ke qareeb) ke paas farishtey aatey hain, agar to wo Saleh shakhs ho to wo kehtey hain : pakizah jism mein pakizah rooh nikal , nikal to qabile-tareef hai, rahat aur rizq ke sath khush ho ja , Rab tujh par naraz nahin, usey isi tarah musalsal kaha jata hai yahan tak ke wo nikal aati hai, phir usey aasmano ki taraf ley jaya jata hai to uskey liye aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain, phir ye puchha jata hai, ye kon hai? wo jawab detey hain, falan hai, to usey kaha jata hai, pakizah jism mein pakizah jaan khush aamadeed , qabile-tareef (rooh) dakhil ho ja , rahat w rizq ke sath khush ho ja , rab tujh par naraz nahin, usey musalsal aisey kaha jata hai yahan tak ke wo us aasman tak pahunch jati hai jahan Allah hai, lekin agar bura shakhs ho to wo (malakul-maut) kehta hai : khabees jism mein basney wali khabees rooh nikal , mazmoom surat mein nikal , kholtey pani aur peep ke sath khush ho ja , aur isi tarah ke miltey jultey doosrey azab bhi, usey aisey hi kaha jata hai yahan tak ke wo nikal aati hai, phir usey aasman ki taraf ley jaya jata hai to uskey liye darwazey kholney ka mutalba hota hai, aur puchha jata hai : ye kon hai? to bataya jata hai : falan hai, usey kaha jata hai : khabees jism mein basney wali khabees rooh ke liye koi khush aamadeed nahin, mazmoom surat mein wapis chali ja , terey liye aasman ke darwazey nahin kholey jaeyngey, usey aasman se chhod diya jata hai, phir wo qabr ki taraf lot aati hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
1628,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab momin ki rooh nikalti hai to do farishtey usey lekar ooper chadhtey hain.'' Hammad (raawi) ne bayan kiya hai, aapney uski acchi khushbu ka zikr kiya aur kastoori ka zikr kiya, farmaya : ''aasman waley kehtey hain, zamin ki taraf se eik pakizah rooh aai hai, Allah tujh par aur us jasad (jism) par, rahmatein nazil farmaai , jis main to abad thi, usey uskey rab ki taraf ley jaya jata hai, phir wo farmata hai : isey aakhiri ajal (qiyamat) tak (iskey maqam par) ley chalo. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab kafir shakhs ki rooh nikalti hai.'' Hammad (raawi) bayan kartey hain aapney uski badboo aur lanat ka zikr kiya, , to aasman waley kehtey hain zamin ki taraf se eik khabees rooh aai hai, to uskey mutalliq bhi kaha jata hai ke usey uski aakhiri ajal tak ley chalo.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney jism waley kapdey ko is tarah apni naak par rakh liya. rawahu Muslim."
1629,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab momin shakhs ki maut ka waqt aata hai to rehmat ke farishtey safed resham lekar aatey hain to wo kehtey hain : razi honey wali pasandida rooh nikal , Allah ki rahat w rizq ki taraf chal , rab tujh par naraz nahin, to wo behtareen kastoori ki khushbu ki tarah nikalti hai yahan tak ke wo eik doosrey se usey letey hain aur isi tarah kartey huey wo usey aasman ke darwazon ke paas ley aatey hain, to wo kehtey hain, zamin se ye kaisi pakizah khushbu tumharey paas aai hai, wo usey mominon ki ruhon ke paas ley aatey hain, to unhen uskey aaney par us se bhi ziyada khushi hoti hai jaisey tum mein se kisi ko apney bichhad janey waley ke milney par khushi hoti hai, wo us se poochhtey hain : falan ka kya haal hai? falan ka kya haal hai? phir wo kehtey hain : usey chhod do , kyonkey wo duniya ke gham mein mubtala tha, to wo (marney wala) kehta hai : wo to (jiskey barey main tum poochh rahey ho) faut ho chuka hai, kya tumharey paas nahin aaya? wo kehtey hain : usey to uskey thikaney ''Hawiya'' (jahannam ka naam) mein pahuncha diya gaya, aur jab kafir shakhs ki maut ka waqt aata hai to azab ke farishtey baalon ka libas lekar uskey paas aatey hain, aur usey kehtey hain : naraz honey wali naa-pasandida rooh nikal aur Shan Wale  Allah ke azab ki taraf chal , wo murdar ki intehai badboo ki surat mein nikalti hai, yahan tak ke wo usey zamin ke darwazey ke paas lekar aatey hain, to wo kehtey hain : ye kitni badbudar hai yahan tak ke wo usey kafiron ki ruhon ke paas ley aatey hain.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Nasai."
1630,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath main eik Ansari shakhs ke janaazey mein shareek huye, ham qabr tak pahunch gaey, abhi lahad tayyar nahin hui thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth gaey to ham bhi aap ke paas beth gaey goya hamarey saron par perindey hon, aap ke haath main eik lakdi thi jis se aap zamin kured rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sar ooper uthaya to farmaya : ''azabe-qabr se Allah ki panah talab karo.'' aapney do ya teen baar aisey farmaya , phir farmaya : ''banda momin jab duniya se rabta tod kar aakhirat ki taraf mutawajjeh hota hai to Suraj ki tarah chamaktey damaktay safed chehron waley farishtey jannati khushbu aur jannati kafan lekar uskey paas aatey hain, yahan tak ke wo hade-nazar tak uskey paas se beth jatey hain, phir malakul-maut (Alaihissalam) tashrif latey hain yahan tak ke wo uskey sar ke paas beth kar kehtey hain, pakizah rooh ! Allah ki maghfirat aur uski razamandi ki taraf chal.'' farmaya : ''wo aisey nikalti hai jaisey mishkeezey se pani ka qatra nikalta hai, wo usey akhaz kar (le) leta hai, jab wo usey akhaz kar leta hai to wo (farishtey) usey aankh jhapakney ke barabar bhi uskey paas nahin chhodtey yahan tak ke wo usey lekar us kafan aur us khushbu mein lapet letey hain, aur phir rooey-zameen par pai janey wali behtareen kastoori ki khushbu us se nikalti hai.'' farmaya : ''wo farishtey usey lekar ooper ki taraf buland hotey hain, aur ye farishton ki jis jamaat ke paas se guzartey hain to wo poochhtey hain ye khushbu kaisi hai? to wo uskey duniya ke namon mein behtareen naam ley ke batatey hain ke ye falan bin falan ki rooh hai yahan tak ke wo usey lekar aasmane-duniya tak pahunchtey hain, aur uskey liye darwaza kholney ki ijazat talab kartey hain, to wo unke liye khol diya jata hai, phir her aasman ke muqarrab farishtey agley aasman tak uskey sath jatey hain yahan tak ke usey saatwen aasman tak pahuncha diya jata hai to  Shan Wala Allah farmata hai : merey bandey ka namae-aamaal illiyin mein likh do aur usey wapis duniya ki taraf ley jaao kyonkey maine inhen usi se paida kiya hai, usi mein inhen lautaaoonga aur dobara phir usi se unhen nikaalunga.'' farmaya : ''uski rooh usi ke jism mein lauta di jati hai to do farishtey uskey paas aatey hain aur usey bitha kar poochhtey hain : tera rab kon hai? to wo kehta hai : mera rab Allah hai, phir wo us se poochhtey hain : tera Deen kya hai? wo kehta hai : mera Deen Islam hai, phir wo poochhtey hain : ye aadmi jo tum mein mab-us kiya (bheja) gaya, kon hai? to wo kehta hai : wo Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain, wo poochhtey hain : tumhen kaisey pata chala? wo kehta hai maine Allah ki kitab padhi to main is par eman laya aur uski tasdeeq ki, isliye aasman se aawaz aati hai : merey bandey ne sach kaha : uskey liye jannati bichhona bichha do, usey jannati libas pehna do aur uskey liye jannat ki taraf eik darwaza khol do.''  farmaya : ''wahaan se hawa ke jhonkey aur khushbu uskey paas aati hai, aur hade-nazar tak uski qabr ko kushada kar diya jata hai.'' farmaya : ''khoobsurat chehrey , khoobsurat libas aur behtareen khushbu wala eik shakhs uskey paas aata hai to wo kehta hai : is chiz se khush ho ja jo chiz tujhey khush kar dey, ye wo din hai jis ka tujh se wada kiya jata tha, to wo us se poochhtey hai : to kon hai? tera chehra bhalai laney wala chehra hai, wo jawab deta hai : main tera amale-saleh hun, wo kehta hai : merey Rab ! qiyamat qaaim farma, merey Rab qiyamat qaaim farma yahan tak ke main apney ehal aur maal ki taraf chala jaaun.'' farmaya : ''jab kafir duniya se rabta munqata' (taud) karkey aakhirat ki taraf tawajjoh karta hai to siyah chehron waley farishtey baalon se bana hua eik kambal lekar aasman se nazil hotey hain, wo us se hade-nazar ke fasley tak beth jatey hain, phir mulk-maut tashrif latey hain yahan tak ke uskey sar ke paas beth jatey hain to wo kehtey hain : khabees rooh ! Allah ki narazi ki taraf chal , farmaya : wo (rooh) uskey jasad (jism) mein phel jati hai, to wo usey aisey khinchtaa hai jaisey lohey ki salaakh ko geeley oon se khincha jata hai, wo (malakul-maut) usey akhaz kar (le) leta hai, jab wo usey akhaz karta hai to wo (farishtey) palak jhapakney ke barabar bhi usey uskey haath mein nahin rehney detey yahan tak ke wo usey us baalon se baney huey kambal mein lapet letey hain, aur us se zamin ke murdar se nikalney wali intehai buri badboo nikalti hai, wo usey lekar ooper chadhtey hain to wo farishton ki jis jamaat ke paas se guzartey hain to wo poochhtey hain, kaisi khabees rooh hai? wo kehtey hain : falan bin falan ki, aur wo uska duniya ka intehai qabeeh (ganda) naam lekar batatey hain, yahan tak ke usey aasmane-duniya tak ley jaya jata hai, uskey liye darwazey kholney ke liye darkhast ki jati hai to uskey liye darwaza nahin khola jata.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''unke liye aasman ke darwaazey nahin kholey jaeyngey aur wo jannat mein bhi dakhil nahin hongey yahan tak ke oont sooi ke surakh mein se guzar jaey.''  Shan Wala Allah farmata hai : ''uski kitab ko sab se nichli zamin mein sijjeen mein likh do, phir uski rooh ko shiddat ke sath phenk diya jata hai.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''jo shakhs Allah ke sath shirk karta hai to goya wo aasman se gir pada , to ab perindey usey uchak lein ya hawa usey kisi door jagah par phenk dey.'' uski rooh uskey jism mein lota di jati hai aur do farishtey uskey paas aatey hain aur us se poochhtey hain : tera rab kon hai? wo herat zada ho kar kehta hai : haaye ! haaye ! main nahin janta , phir wo us se poochhtey hain : tera Deen kya hai? to wo herat zada ho kar kehta hai : haaye ! afsos ! main nahin janta , phir wo poochhtey hain : ye shakhs jo tum mein mab-us kiya (bheja) gaya kon hai? to wo kehta hai : haaye ! afsos ! main nahin janta , aasman se aawaz aati hai, isney jhoot bola , uskey liye jahannam se bichhona bichha do , aur uskey liye jahannam ki taraf eik darwaza khol do , wahan se garmi aur garm hawa usey aati rahegi aur uski qabr ko is qadr tang kar diya jaeyga ke uski pasliyan eik dusri ke andar dakhil ho jaeyn gi, aur eik qabeeh chehrey (bad-shakl) wala shakhs , qabeeh (gande) libas aur intehai badbudar haalat mein uskey paas aaeyga aur usey kahega : tumhen aisi chizon ki khushkhabri ho jo tujhey gham zada kar den , ye tera wo din hai jis ka tujh se wada kiya jata tha, wo puchheyga to kon hai? terey chehrey se kisi khair ki tawaqqo nahin, wo jawab dega : main tera khabees amal hun, to wo kahega : merey rab ! qiyamat qaaim na karna.'' eik dusri riwayat mein bhi isi tarah hai lekin is mein ye izafa hai : ''jab us (momin) ki rooh nikalti hai to zamin aur aasman ke beech aur aasman ke tamam farishtey uskey liye rehmat ki dua talab kartey hain, uskey liye aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain, her darwazey waley Allah se dua kartey hain ke uski rooh unki taraf se buland ki jaey, aur us yani kafir ki rooh ragon samet kheenchi jati hai aur zamin aur aasman ke beech waley tamam farishtey aur aasman waley tamam farishtey is par lanat kartey hain, aasman ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur tamam darbaan farishtey Allah se dua kartey hain ke uski rooh ko hamari taraf se buland na kiya jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed."
1631,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kab apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke jab Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ka waqt hua to Umme-Bishr binte Bara bin Ma'roor (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas aaeen, to unhoney kaha : Abu-Abdur-Rehman ! agar tum falan (unke baap Bara ki rooh) se mulaqat karo to usey mera salam kehna, unhoney kaha : Umme-Bashir ! Allah aap ko maaf farmaai , hamein uski fursat kahan miley gi, Umme- Bashir ne farmaya : Abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey nahin suna : ''mominon ki roohen sabz (hara) parindon (ke jism mein) jannat ke darakhton se khati hongi.'' unhoney kaha : haan ! suna hai. to Umme-Bashir ne farmaya : isliye yehi wo hai."
1632,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kab apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke wo bayan kiya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin ki rooh perindey ki shakal mein jannat ke darkht se khati hai yahan tak ke Allah jis roz usey uthaeyga to usey uskey jism mein lauta dega.'' rawahu Maalik, Nasai aur Al-Behaqi."
1633,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Munkadir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) par nazaa (jaan nikalne) ka aalim taari tha to main unke paas gaya to maine unhen kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam kehna. rawahu ibne-Maja."
1634,"Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye jabkey ham aap ki beti ko ghusl dey rahi thin, aapney farmaya : ''usey teen ya paanch martaba ya agar us se ziyada martaba tum zarurat mehsus karo to pani aur beri ke patton se ghusl do aur aakhiri martaba kaafur ya kaafur jaisi koi chiz is mein mila lo , jab tum farigh ho jaao to mujhey muttala (ittilaa) karna.'' jab ham farigh ho gaeen to ham ne aap ko muttala kar diya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni chadar hamari taraf phenk kar farmaya isey uskey jism par dal do.'' (phir us chadar ke ooper kafan pehnaao) aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''usey taaq adad teen ya paanch ya saat martaba ghusl do , daain taraf aur wuzu ki jagahon se shuru karo.'' aur unhoney (yani umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : ham ne uskey baalon ki teen chotiyan goondhin aur unhen uskey peechhey dal diya. muttafaq aleh."
1635,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Yamen ke teen safed sooti kapdon mein kafan diya gaya, jin mein qameez thi na amaamaa. muttafaq aleh."
1636,"Hazrat Jabir bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney bhai ko kafan dey to usey behtar tareeqey se kafan dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
1637,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi haalate-ehram mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha to uski oontni ne usey nichey gira kar uski gardan tod di, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey pani aur beri ke patton se ghusl do usey uskey inhin (ehram ke) do kapdon mein kafan do, aur isey khushbu lagaao na iskey sar ko dhaanpo kyonkey wo qiyamat ke roz talbiya pukarta hua utheyga.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur ham Musab bin Umer (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ke mutalliq Khabbab (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees Jaame al Manaqib ke silsile mein In-sha-Allah taala bayan karengey. muttafaq aleh."
1638,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safed kapdey pehna karo kyonkey wo tumhara behtareen libas hai, apney mardon ko bhi unhin mein kafan do, asmad tumhara behtareen surma hai kyonkey wo palke daraz (lambi) karta hai aur nazar ko tez karta hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur ibne-Maja ne ''apney mardon ko'' tak riwayat kiya hai."
1639,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mehngaa kafan na diya karo kyonkey wo to jald hi boseedah ho jata hai.''"
1640,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab wo qaribul-marg (maut ke qareeb) huey to unhoney naya libas mangwaa kar pehna , phir farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''maiyat ko uskey unhin kapdon mein uthaya jaeyga jin mein usey maut aai hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1641,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''joda (izaar aur chadar) behtareen kafan hai jabkey seengon wala mendhaa behtareen qurbani hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1642,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi aur Imam ibne-Maja ne isey Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai.
1643,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shohdaaey uhud ke barey mein farmaya : '' unke chamdey ki posteenein (ooni chadaren waghera) aur hathiyar utaar lo aur unko khoon samet unke kapdon mein dafn kar do.''"
1644,"Hazrat Saad bin Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) rozey se they ke (iftaar ke liye) unke paas khana laya gaya to unhoney farmaya : Musab bin Umer (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid kar diye gaey jabkey wo mujh se behtar they, unhen eik chadar mein kafan diya gaya, agar unka sar dhanpa jata to unke paaon nangey ho jatey aur agar unke paaon dhaanpey jatey to unka sar nanga ho jata. raawi kehtey hain, mera khayal hai ke unhoney farmaya : Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid kar diye gaey jabkey wo mujh se behtar they, phir ham par duniya ki nematen wafir (bahut ziyada) kar di gaeen, ya farmaya : hamein bahut ziyada duniya ka maal aur mataa ata kar diya gaya ke hamein andesha hua ke hamari nekiyon ka badla hamein duniya hi mein dey diya gaya hai, phir unhoney ronaa shuru kar diya yahan tak ke khana bhi tarak kar diya. Bukhari."
1645,"Hazrat Jabir Bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abdullah bin Ubai ke paas aaye jabkey usey qabr mein utaar diya gaya tha, aap ke hukm par usey bahar nikala gaya, aapney usey apney ghutnon par rakha , aur uskey jism par apna lab Mubarak thooka aur usey apni qameez pahnaai, raawi bayan kartey hain, aur us (Abdullah bin Ubai) ne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko qameez pahnaai thi. muttafaq aleh."
1646,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''janaza jaldi ley jaya karo, agar to wo Saleh hai to phir tum usey bhalai ki taraf ley ja rahey ho, aur agar wo uskey ilawa hai to phir wo eik shar hai jisey tum apni gardanon se utaar rahey ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
1647,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab janaazey ko rakha jata hai aur log usey kandhon par utha letey hain to agar wo nek ho to kehta hai : mujhey aagey pohchaao aur agar wo Saleh na ho to wo apney ghar walon se kehta hai : tabahi ho, tum mujhey kahan ley ja rahey ho. insan ke ilawa her chiz uski aawaz sunti hai, aur agar insan sun ley to wo be-hosh ho jaey.'' Bukhari."
1648,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum janaza dekho to khadey ho jaao , aur jo shakhs uskey sath jaey to wo us waqt tak na bethey yahan tak ke usey rakh diya jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1649,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik janaza guzra to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho gaey aur ham bhi aap ke sath khadey ho gaey, phir ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye to eik Yahudi aurat ka janaza hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : maut ghabrahat wali chiz hai, jab tum janaza dekho to khadey ho jaao.'' muttafaq aleh."
1650,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko janaza dekh kar khadey hotey dekha to ham bhi khadey ho gaey aur ham ne aap ko bethtey dekha to ham bhi beth gaey . aur Imam Malik aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : aap janaza dekh kar khadey ho gaey phir uskey baad aap beth gaey. rawahu Muslim, Malik aur Abu-Dawood."
1651,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs eman aur sawab ki niyat se kisi musalman ke janaazey mein shareek hota hai, uskey sath rehta hai yahan tak ke uski Namaze-janaza padhi jati hai aur uskey dafnaney se farigh ho jata hai to wo do qiraat ajr ke sath wapis aata hai, her qiraat uhad pahad ki jaisi hai, aur jo shakhs Namaze-janaza padhta hai aur uskey dafn honey se pehley wapis aa jata hai to wo eik qraat ajr ke sath wapis aata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1652,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Najashi ke faut honey ki, jis roz wo faut huye, khabar sunai aur aap Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar eid gaah tashrif ley gaey, aapney unki safein banaeen aur chaar takbeerein kahin. muttafaq aleh."
1653,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Laila bayan kartey hain, Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) Namaze-janaza mein chaar takbeerein kaha kartey they, jabkey eik janaazey par unhoney paanch takbeerein kahin to ham ne un se sawal kiya. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey bhi kaha kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
1654,"Hazrat Talha bin Abdullah bin Auf bayan kartey hain, maine ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey Namaze-janaza padhi to unhoney (buland aawaz sey) Sura Fatiha padhi. baad iske farmaya : taake tum jaan lo ke ye sunnat hai. Bukhari."
1655,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaze-janaza padhi to maine aap ki dua yad kar li , aap keh rahey they : ''aey Allah ! isey maaf farma , iski behtareen mehman nawaazi farma , iski qabr faraakh farma , iskey gunah pani , olon aur barf se dho dal, isey gunahon se is tarah saaf kar dey jaisey to ne safed kapdey ko mail se saaf kiya hai, isey iskey (duniya waley) ghar se behtar ghar (duniya ke) ehal se behtar ehal (khaadim waghera) aur (duniya ki) zauja (biwi) se behtar zauja (biwi) ata farma, isey jannat mein dakhil farma aur azabe-qabr isike saath azabe-jahannam se mehfooz rakh.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''isey fitnae-qabr aur azabe-jahannam se mehfooz farma.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : (aapney is qadr duaeyn keen) ke maine tamanna ki ke kaash! ! ye maiyat meri hoti. rawahu Muslim."
1656,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai ke jab Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ne wafat pai to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : unhen masjid mein ley aao taake main bhi unki Namaze-janaza padh sakun , lekin unki ye baat qubul na ki gaee , to unhoney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baizaa ke do beton , Suhel aur uskey bhai ki Namaze-janaza masjid mein padhi thi. rawahu Muslim."
1657,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey , haalate-nifaas mein faut ho janey wali aurat ki, Namaze-janaza padhi, to aap uskey beech mein khadey huey. muttafaq aleh."
1658,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik qabr ke paas se guzrey jahan guzishta raat kisi ko dafn kiya gaya tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kab dafn kiya gaya?'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, guzishta (pichhli) raat. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne mujhey kyon na muttala kiya (ittila di)?'' unhoney arz kiya : ham ne raat ki taareeki mein usey dafn kiya tha, isliye ham ne aap ko bedaar karna munasib na samjha , isliye aap khadey huey to ham ne aap ke peechhey safein baandhin , phir aapney uski Namaze-janaza padhi. muttafaq aleh."
1659,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik siyah rang khatoon , jo ke masjid ki safai kiya karti thin ya koi nojawan tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey na dekha to aapney uskey barey mein sawal kiya, Sahaba ne arz kiya, wo to wafat pa chuka. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne mujhey kyon na ittila di?'' raawi bayan kartey hain, goya unhoney uskey mamley ko kam tar samjha . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey uski qabr bataao.'' unhoney bata diya to aapney wahan Namaze-janaza padhi, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye qabren apney as-haab (saathiyon) par andheron se bhari padi hain, aur be-shak Allah merey Namaze-janaza padhney ke zariey unhen munawwar (roshan) farma deta hai.'' Bukhari , Muslim aur alfaz Sahih Muslim ke hain. muttafaq aleh."
1660,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam Kuraib, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain qudaid ya Asfan ke maqam par unka beta faut ho gaya. unhoney farmaya : Kureb ! dekho , iskey (janaazey) ke liye kitney log jama ho chukey hain? raawi bayan kartey hain, main bahar aaya to dekha ke log jama ho chukey they, maine aap ko bataya to unhoney puchha : wo chaalis hain? unhoney kaha : ji haan , phir ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : isey ley chalo , kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo musalman faut ho jaey aur phir chaalis muwahhid (jo Allah ka shareek nahin thehratey) uski Namaze-janaza padh lein to Allah us shakhs ke barey mein unki shafaat qubul farmata hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1661,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis maiyat par sau musalman janaza padhein aur wo tamam uskey haq mein sifarish karen to uskey haq mein unki sifarish qubul ki jati hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1662,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, wo eik janaazey ke paas se guzrey to unhoney uski achchhai bayan ki, jis par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wajib ho gaee.'' phir wo doosrey janaazey ke paas se guzrey to unhoney uski burai bayan ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wajib ho gaee.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : kya wajib ho gaee? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne uski achchhai bayan ki to uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee aur jiski tum ne burai bayan ki to uskey liye jahannam wajib ho gaee, tum zamin par Allah ke gawah ho.'' Bukhari , Muslim aur eik riwayat mein hai, momin zamin par Allah ke gawah hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1663,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis musalman ke barey mein chaar aadmi gawahi dey den ke wo achchha hai to Allah usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga.'' ham ne arz kiya : aur teen aadmi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen aadmi.'' ham ne arz kiya : do aadmi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do aadmi.'' phir ham ne eik ke barey mein aap se nahin poochha. Bukhari."
1664,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''faut ho jaane wale ko bura bhala mat kaho , kyonkey wo to apni saza pa chukey.'' Bukhari."
1665,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shohdaaey uhad ke do-do aadmiyon ko eik kapdey mein ikhatta kartey aur farmatey ''in mein se Quran ka ilm kis ko ziyada tha? ''jab un mein se kisi eik ki taraf ishara kar diya jata to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey pehley lahad mein utaartey, aur farmatey : ''main roze-qiyamat in logon ki gawahi dunga.'' aapney unhen usi khoon aalooda haalat mein dafn karney ka hukm farmaya, aapney unki Namae-janaza padhi na unhen ghusl diya gaya. Bukhari."
1666,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ibne Dah'daah ki Namaze-janaza se farigh huey to zeen ke baghair eik ghoda aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya jis par aap Sawar ho gaey jabkey ham aap ke ird-gird pedal chaltey rahey. rawahu Muslim."
1667,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sawwaar shakhs janaazey ke peechhey jabkey pedal chalney wala uskey peechhey , uskey aagaey, uskey daain aur uskey baain uskey qarib qarib chaleyga , aur namukammal paida honey waley bachchey ki Namaze janaza padhi jaeygi aur uskey waliden ke liye maghfirat aur rehmat ki dua ki jaeygi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Ahmed aur Tirmizi. Ahmed, Tirmizi, Nasai aur ibne-Maja ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sawwaar janaazey ke peechhey jabkey piyaada jis taraf chahey chal sakta hai, aur bachchey ki Namaze-janaza padhi jaeygi.'' Masaabih mein Mughira bin Ziyad se marwi (bayan) hai."
1668,"Hazrat Zohri, Salim se aur wo apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko janaazey ke aagey chaltey huey dekha. Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai , ibne-Maja , Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : aur muhaddeseen isey mursal samajhtey hain."
1669,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''janaazey ke peechhey chalna chahiye, uskey aagey nahin chalna chahiye aur jo shakhs uskey aagey chalta hai to wo (sharae lihaz sey) uskey sath nahin.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja, Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : Abu Majid raawi majhool hai."
1670,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs janaazey ke sath chaley aur teen martaba usey uthaey to usney apney zimmey uskey haq ko ada kar diya.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1671,Hazrat Sharahus-Sunnah mein marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke janaazey ko do paayon ke darmiyan se uthaya. ( لا اصل لہ ).
1672,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath main eik janaze mein shareek huey . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko sawaariyon par dekha to farmaya : ''kya tumhen haya nahin aati ke Allah ke farishtey to pedal hain aur tum sawaariyon par ho.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , aur Abu-Dawood ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kiya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se moquf riwayat ki gaee hai."
1673,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaze-janaza mein Sura Fatiha padhi.
1674,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum janaza padho to maiyat ke liye khulus ke sath dua karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
1675,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaze-janaza padhtey to ye dua farmatey : ''aey Allah ! hamarey zindon , hamarey mardon , hamarey mojud aur hamarey ghair mojud , hamarey chhoton aur hamarey badon hamarey mardon aur hamari aurton ki maghfirat farma , aey Allah ! to ham mein se jisey zinda rakhey to usey Islam par zinda rakh aur to ham mein se jisey faut karey to usey eman par faut karna, aey Allah ! hamein iskey ajr se mehroom karna na iskey baad hamein fitney ka shikar karna.'' rawahu Ahmed, Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi ibne-Maja."
1676,"Aur Imam Nasai ne Ibrahim Ash'hali an Abi ki sanad se riwayat kiya hai, aur unki riwayat hamari aurton ko ''maaf farma'' tak khatam ho jati hai, aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : ''isey eman par zinda rakh aur Islam par faut kar.'' aur uskey aakhir mein hai : ''iskey baad hamein gumrah na karna.''"
1677,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi musalman shakhs ki Namaze-janaza padhaai to maine aap ko ye dua kartey huey suna : ''aey Allah ! falan terey zimmey aur teri rehmat ke saye mein hai, isey fitnae-qabr aur azabe-jahannam se bacha, to ehale wafaa aur ehale haq hai, aey Allah ! iski maghfirat farma, is par rehem farma , be-shak to bakhshney wala rehem karney wala hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
1678,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney faut hone wale ki khoobiyan bayan kiya karo aur unki buraiyan bayan karney se ijtinab (bacha) karo.''"
1679,"Hazrat Naafe Abu Ghalib (Reh.) bayan kartey hain, maine Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath eik aadmi ki Namaze-janaza padhi to wo uskey sar ke muqabil khadey huye, phir eik Quraishi khatoon ka janaza aaya to unhoney kaha : aey Abu-Hamza ! iski Namaze-janaza padho , isliye wo uski chaarpai ke beech mein khadey huye, to Ala bin Ziyad ne un se puchha : kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah dekha hai ke aap aurat ka janaza padhatey waqt is jagah (chaarpai ke beech mein) khadey huey they aur eik aadmi ki Namaze-janaza padhatey waqt is jagah khadey huey they jahan aap khadey huey hain? unhoney farmaya : haan. Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. Abu-Dawood ki eik riwayat mein isi tarah hai, is mein kuchh izafa hai, ke aap (aurat ki Namaze-janaza padhatey waqt) aurat ke peeth ke paas khadey huey. rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , Abu-Dawood."
1680,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi-Laila bayan kartey hain, Suhel bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) aur Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) qaadsiya mein tashrif farma they ke unke paas se eik janaza guzra to wo dono khadey ho gaey, unhen bataya gaya ke ye zimmi shakhs ka janaza hai, un dono ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se eik janaza guzra to aap khadey ho gaey aap ko bataya gaya ke ye eik Yahudi ka janaza hai, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wo jaan nahin?'' muttafaq aleh."
1681,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi janaazey mein shareek hotey to aap maiyat ko lahad mein utaarney tak nahin bethtey they, eik Yahudi aalim aap ke paas aaya to usney aap se kaha, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! be-shak ham bhi aisey hi kartey hain. raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth gaey, aur farmaya : ''inki mukhalifat karo.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja. Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, Bashir bin Raafe raawi qawi nahin."
1682,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne janaza dekh kar hamein khada honey ka hukm farmaya , uskey baad phir aap beth gaey to aapney hamein beth janey ka hukm farmaya. rawahu Ahmed."
1683,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Seerin bayan kartey hain, Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se eik janaza guzra to Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho gaey lekin ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) khadey na huey to Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Yahudi ke janaazey ke liye khadey nahin huey they? unhoney farmaya : haan, (lekin) phir aap bethey rehtey they. rawahu Nasai."
1684,"Hazrat Jaafar bin Muhammad apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bethey huey they ke unke paas se eik janaza guzra to log khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke janaza guzar gaya, to Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : eik Yahudi ka janaza guzra jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey raastey par bethey huey they, aapney is baat ko napasand farmaya ke kisi Yahudi shakhs ka janaza aap ke sar Mubarak se buland ho jaey lihaza aap khadey ho gaey. rawahu Nasai."
1685,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumharey paas se kisi Yahudi ya kisi nasrani ya kisi musalman ka janaza guzrey to tum uskey liye khadey ho jaao , tum uskey liye nahin khadey ho rahey balke tum to un farishton ke liye khadey huey ho jo us (janaazey) ke sath hain.''"
1686,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se eik janaza guzra to aap khadey ho gaey, aap ko bataya gaya ke ye to kisi Yahudi ka janaza hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main to sirf farishton ki khatir khada hua hun.''"
1687,"Hazrat Maalik bin Hubaira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''koi musalman faut ho jaey aur musalmanon ki teen safein uski Namaze-janaza padh-den to uskey liye (jannat) wajib ho jati hai.'' jab Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) dekhtey ke janaza padhney waley kam hain to aap is hadees ki buniyad par unhen teen safon mein taqseem farma detey they. Abu-Dawood. Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai ke jab Malik bin Hubaira (Raziallahu anhu) koi Namaze-janaza padhtey aur janaza padhney waley kam hotey to wo unhen teen hisson mein taqseem farma detey, phir bayan kartey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs par teen safein Namaze-janaza padhein to is par (jannat) wajib ho gaee.'' aur ibne-Maja ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
1688,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Namaze-janaza ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah ! to iska rab hai, to ne isey paida farmaya , tu ney isey Islam ki raah dikhai , to ne iski rooh qabz kar li aur to iskey zahir w baatin se waqif hai, ham sifarishi bin kar aaye hain, iski maghfirat farma.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1689,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey eik aisey bachchey ki Namaze-janaza padhi jisney kabhi koi gunah kya hi nahin, wo dua kar rahey they : ''aey Allah ! isey azabe-qabr se bachcha ley.'' rawahu Malik."
1690,"Hazrat Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne muallaq riwayat bayan kartey huey farmaya : Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) bachey ki Namaz janaza mein Sura Fatiha padhtey aur ye dua kartey : aey Allah ! usey hamarey liye pesh ro, meer manzil, zakhira aur sawab bana .''"
1691,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak paida honey wala bacha cheekhey nahin tab tak uski Namaz janaza padhi jaeygi na wo waris banega aur na hi uski meeras taqseem hogi.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, lekin unhoney ye zikr nahin kya ke '' uski meeras taqseem nahin hogi .''"
1692,"Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Imam ko kisi buland jagah par khadey honey se mana farmaya jabkey muqtadi uskey nichey hun."
1693,Hazrat Aamir bin Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ne apney marz wafat mein farmaya : merey liye lahad tayyar karna aur is par entein khadi karna jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ki qabr) ke sath kya gaya. rawahu Muslim.
1694,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr main eik surkh chadar bichhaai gaee thi. rawahu Muslim ."
1695,Hazrat Sufiyan Tammar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr ko kohan ki tarah dekha. Bukhari .
1696,"Hazrat abul-Hayyaj Asadii (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey farmaya : kya main tumhen aisey kaam par maamoor na karun jis par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey maamoor w Nabi banakar bheja tha, ke tum her murti ko mita do aur her oonchi qabr ko barabar kar do. rawahu Muslim."
1697,"Hazrat Jabir bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qabr ko pukhta bananey, is par imarat bananey aur us par) mujaawir (bin kar bethney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Muslim ."
1698,"Hazrat Abu-Marsad ghanwii (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qabron par) mujaawir bin kar) betho na unki taraf rukh karkey Namaz padho .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1699,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum mein se koi shakhs aag ke angaarey par beth jaey, wo kapdey ko jala kar uski jild tak pahunch jaey to ye uskey liye qabr par bethney se behtar hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1700,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber bayan kartey hain, Madina mein do gorkan they, un mein se eik lehad banata tha jabkey doosra lehad tayyar nahin karta tha, Sahaba ne farmaya : un dono mein se jo pehley aaeyga wo apna kaam kerega, pas lehad bananey wala shakhs pehley aaya to phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye lehad tayyar ki gaee. ( rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
1701,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hamarey ( musalmanon ke) liye lehad hai aur shaqq ( dahaane ki shakal wali qabr ( hamarey ilawa dusron ke liye hai.''"
1702,aur Imam Ahmed ne Jarir bin Abdullah se riwayat kya hai.
1703,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-ahad ke roz farmaya : '' wasee aur gehri qabren tayyar karo aur achi tarah dafn karo, aur eik qabr mein do-do, teen-teen ko dafn karo, aur un mein se ziyada Quran janney waley ko pehley dafn karo.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai aur ibne-Maja ne ( واحسنوا ( '' aur achi tarah dafn karo '' tak riwayat kya hai."
1704,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae-ahad ke roz meri phuphi merey Shaheed walid ko ley aain taake wo unhen hamarey qabristaan mein dafn karen, pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se aelan karney waley ne aelan kya, shaheedon ko unki shahadat gaah ki taraf wapis ley aao.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai, Darmi, alfaz hadees Tirmizi ke hain."
1705,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sar ki janib se qabr mein utara gaya."
1706,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke waqt eik qabr mein dakhil huey to aap ke liye chiragh roshan kya gaya, aapney ( maiyat ko) qible ki taraf se liya, aur farmaya : ''Allah tum par rehem farmaey, tum bahut ziyada tazree (girya wzaari) karney waley aur bahut ziyada Quran ki tilawat karney waley they.'' Tirmizi, aur unhon (Imam Baghwi ( ne Sharahus-sunnah mein farmaya : iski sanad zaeef hai."
1707,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab maiyat ko qabr mein dakhil kya jata to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yun farmatey : ''Allah ke naam ke sath, Allah ki tofiq ke sath aur Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki millat w Deen par.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke tareeqey par.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, aur Abu-Dawood ne dusri riwayat bayan ki hai."
1708,"Hazrat Jaafar bin Muhammad (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se mursal riwayat bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dono haath mila kar maiyat (yani qabr) par teen lap mitti dali, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney bete Ibrahim ki qabr par pani chhidka aur is par kankariyaan rakhin. Sharahus-sunnah, aur Imam Shafai ne ''pani chhidakney'' ke alfaz riwayat kiye."
1709,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qabron ke pukhta kerney, un par likhney ( katbey laganey (aur unhen raundney se mana farmaya. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1710,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr par pani chhidka gaya, Bilal bin Ribah (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik mishkeezey ke zariey aap ki qabr par pani chhidka, unhoney aap ke sar Mubarak ki taraf se chhidakna shuru kya aur aap ke paaon tak chhidaktey gaey."
1711,"Hazrat Muttalib bin abi wdaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ne wafat pai , unka janaza laya gaya, jab unhen dafn kar diya gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko hukm farmaya ke wo eik pathar aap ke paas laye, wo aadmi usey na utha saka to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khud uth kar us taraf gaey aapney aasteenein ooper chadhaaein , Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jis shakhs ne mujhey waqia bayan kya, usney kaha, goya main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baazuon ki safedi dekh raha hun jab aapney aasteenein uthai thin, phir aapney us pathar ko uthaya aur usey un ( Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sar ke paas rakh kar farmaya : ''main uskey zariey apney bhai ki qabr ke barey mein bataaunga aur apney khandan mein faut honey waley shakhs ko uskey qarib dafn karunga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1712,"Hazrat Qasim bin Muhammad bayan kartey hain, main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya to maine kaha : maa ji ! mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke dono sathiyon ki qabren to dikha den, unhoney mujhey teeno qabren dikha din, wo buland thin na zamin ke barabar thin aur un par maqam arsa ke surkh sangrezey bichhaaey huey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1713,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath main eik Ansari shakhs ke janaazey mein shareek huye, ham qabr par pahunch gaey, lekin abhi lehad tayyar nahin hui thi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qibla rukh ho kar beth gaey aur ham bhi aap ke sath beth gaey . Abu-Dawud, Nasai , ibne-Maja , aur unhoney hadees ke aakhir mein ye izafa naqal kya hai : goya hamarey saron par perindey hon."
1714,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' maiyat ki haddi ka todna, zinda ki haddi ke todney ke mutraadif hai.'' rawahu Malik w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
1715,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sahibzadi ki tadfeen ke waqt ham mojud they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabr ke paas tashrif farma they, maine aap ki aakhon ko ashkbar dekha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mein koi aisa shakhs hai jisney aaj raat apni ehliya se sohbat na ki ho?'' abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, main ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aap uski qabr mein utren.'' wo unki qabr mein utrey. Bukhari."
1716,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne , jab wo nazaa (jism se jaan nikalney) ke aalim mein they, apney bete se kaha : jab main faut ho jaaun to merey sath koi nauha karney wali jaey na aag, jab tum mujhey dafn kar chuko aur mujh par mitti dal lo to phir itni der tak meri qabr ke gird khadey rehna jitni der mein oont zibeh karkey uska gosht taqseem kya jata hai, yahan tak ke main tumhari wajeh se khush aur pursukoon hun aur main jaan lun ke main apney rab ke bhejey huey qaasidon (farishton) ko kya jawab deta hun.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1717,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab tum mein se koi faut ho jaey to usey (dafn karney sey) na rok rakho, balke usey jald dafn karo . aur) dafn karney ke baad) sarhaaney Sura Baqra ka ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey aur uskey paaon ke paas Sura Baqra ka aakhiri hissey padha jaey.'' ( Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( , aur unhoney ne farmaya : durust baat ye hai ke ye moquf hai."
1718,"Hazrat ibne-abi Muleka bayan kartey hain. jab Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mauza Hubshi mein wafat pai to unhen Makka la kar dafn kya gaya, jab Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) wahan tashrif laeyn to wo Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ki qabr par aain aur ye ashaar kahey : ham Jazima ke dono sathiyon ki tarah eik muddat tak miley juley rahey, yahan tak ke ye kaha janey laga ke ye dono kabhi juda nahin hongey, jab ham juda huey to goya main aur Malik taweel muddat tak ikhatta rehney ke baad bhi aisey they jaisey ham eik raat bhi ikhattey na rahey they. phir unhoney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! agar main mojud hoti to tumhen jaey wafat par hi dafn kya jata, aur agar main tumhari wafat ke waqt mojud hoti to main tumhari ziyaarat karney na aati . rawahu Tirmizi ."
1719,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Saad ko sar ki taraf se qabr mein utaara, aur unki qabr par pani chhidka."
1720,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik Namaz janaza padhi, phir qabr par tashrif laye aur uskey sar ki janib se is par teen lap mitti dali."
1721,"Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey eik qabr par tek lagaey huey dekha to farmaya : '' us qabr waley ko ya usko takleef na pahunchaao.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
1722,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein abu-Yusuf Haddaad jo ke) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bete ( Ibrahim ke doodh shareek baap they, ke paas gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ibrahim ko ley liya , usey chooma aur soongha, ham uskey baad phir unke paas gaey to Ibrahim aakhiri saanson par they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aankhen ashkbar ho gaeen to Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap ( bhi rotey hain ( , aapney farmaya : '' ibne-Auf ! ye to rehmat hai.'' aur phir aap dobara roey aur farmaya be-shak aankhen ashkbar aur dil ghamgin hai, lekin ham sirf wohi baat karengey jis se hamara parwardigar razi ho. aey Ibrahim ! ham teri judai par yaqinan ghamgin hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1723,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki lakht jigar ne aap ki taraf pegham bheja ke mera beta qaribul-marg (maut ke qareeb) hai, lihaza aap tashrif laeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam bheja aur ye pegham diya : ''yaqeenan Allah ka hai jo usney ley liya , aur jo usney dey rakha hai, uskey haan her chiz ka waqt muqarrar hai, pas sabr karen aur sawab paeyn .''unhoney dobaara pegham bheja aur qism de-kar arz kya ke aap zarur tashrif laeyn , aap khadey huey aur Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) , Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) , Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) , Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) , aur kuch aur log aap ke sath tashrif laye, bachey ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki god mein dey diya gaya, jabke uskey saanson ka rabt toot raha tha, aap ki aankhen ashkbar ho gaeen to Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye kya hua ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye (aansu) to Allah ki rehmat hai jo Allah ne apney bandon ke dilon mein paida farmaai, Allah bhi apney rehem karney waley bandon par hi rehem farmaata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1724,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) kisi bimari mein mubtala huey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye jabkey Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu), Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath they, jab aap unke paas pahunchey to aapney unhen behoshi ke aalim mein paya to farmaya : ''kya ye faut ho chukey ?'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! nahin, pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) roney lagey, jab logon ne aap ko rotey huey dekha to wo bhi ro diye , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum suntey nahin ke Allah aakhon ke roney aur dil ke ghamgin honey par azab nahin deta , lekin wo to is zaban ki wajeh se azab deta hai ya rehem karta hai, aur be-shak maiyat ko, uskey ehle khana ke is par roney ki wajeh se azab diya jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1725,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs rukhsaar peetey, gareban chaak karey aur jahiliyat ki si baaten karey to wo ham mein se nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
1726,"Hazrat abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) par be-hoshi taari ho gaee to unki ehliya Umme- Abdullah ne zor se rona shuru kar diya, phir unhen ifaaqa ho gaya to farmaya : ''kya tumhen malum nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aisey shakhs se bari hun jo musibat ke waqt sar mundaaey, oonchi aawaz se roey aur kapdey chaak karey.'' Bukhari, Muslim aur hadees ke alfaz sahih Muslim ke hain. muttafaq aleh."
1727,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein jahiliyat ki chaar khaslatein aisi hain jinhen wo nahin chodengey, hasab par fakhr karna, nasab par ta'an karna, sitaron ke zariey barish talab karna aur nauha karna '' aur farmaya : ''jo nauha karney wali maut se pehley tauba na karey to roze-qiyamat is par gandhak ki qameez hogi aur khaarish ka kurta hoga .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1728,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik aurat ke paas se guzar hua jo eik qabr ke paas ro rahi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah se dar aur sabr kar .'' usney kaha : mujh se door raho , kyonkey tum meri musibat se do-chaar nahin huye, usney aap ko dekh kar na pehchaana to usey bataya gaya ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain, pas wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke darwazey par hazir hui to usney dekha ke wahan koi darbaan nahin tha, usney arz kya : main aap ko pehchan nahin saki , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sabr to ibtadaaey sadma ke waqt hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1729,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis musalman ke teen bachey faut ho jaeyn to wo sirf qism puri karney ki khatir hi jahannam mein jaeyga ( wo bhi pal siraat se guzartey waqt ( .'' muttafaq aleh."
1730,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ansaar ki khawatin se farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi ke teen bachey faut ho jaeyn aur wo us se sawab talab karey to wo jannat mein dakhil hogi , un mein se kisi aurat ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya do par bhi ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do par bhi .'' Muslim , aur sahihain ki riwayat mein hai : '' teen nabaligh bachey .'' rawahu Muslim w Bukhari."
1731,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : jab main apney momin bandey ki ehle duniya se kisi mehbub chiz ko uthata hun aur wo is par sabr karta hai to uski merey yahan jaza jannat ke siwa aur kuch nahin .'' Bukhari ."
1732,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nauha karney wali aur qasdan usey sunney wali par lanat farmaai ."
1733,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin ki ajeeb shaan hai, agar usey koi khair w bhalai nasib hoti hai to Allah ki hamd bayan karta aur shukr karta hai, aur agar usey koi musibat pahunchti hai to bhi Allah ki hamd bayan karta hai aur sabr karta hai, pas momin apney ( shukr w sabr ke) her mamley mein ajr paata hai, yahan tak ke us luqme par bhi jo wo apni ehliya ke munh mein daalta hai.'' , ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
1734,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her momin ke liye do darwazey hain, eik darwazey se uskey aamaal ooper chadhtey hain aur eik darwazey se uska rizq nazil hota hai, jab wo faut ho jata hai to wo dono is par rotey hain, pas ye Allah Taala ka farman hai : '' un par aasman roya na zamin .''"
1735,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein se jis shakhs ke do bachey pesh ro hun (yani faut ho jaeyn ( to Allah unki wajeh se usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga .'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya, aap ki ummat mein se jis ka eik pesh ro ho? aapney farmaya : '' jis ko tofiq di gaee ho ! jiska eik pesh ro ho ( wo bhi jannati hai) .'' unhoney arz kya, aap ki ummat mein se jis ka eik bhi pesh ro na ho? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main apni ummat ka pesh ro hunga, unhen meri misl koi takleef nahin pahunchaai gaee.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1736,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab bandey ka bacha faut ho jaata hai to Allah Taala farishton se farmata hai : kya tum ne merey bandey ke bachey (ki rooh) ko qabz kar liya? wo arz kartey hain, ji haan, phir wo poochhtey hain: kya tum ne uskey samar qalb (jigar goshe ki rooh) ko qabz kar liya? wo arz kartey hain, ji haan, Allah farmata hai ke merey bandey ne kya kaha tha? wo arz kartey hain, usney teri hamd bayan ki aur (inna lillahi w-inna ilaihi raajioon) padha tha, phir Allah farmata hai : merey bandey ke liye jannat main eik ghar bana do aur uska naam baitul-Hamd rakho.''"
1737,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi musibat zada shakhs ko tasalli deta hai to usey bhi uski misl ajr milta hai.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur ham Ali bin Aasim se marwi (bayan) hadees se usey marfoo jantey hain, aur unhoney (Imam Tirmizi ( ne farmaya : un mein se baaz ne usey Muhammad bin sooqa se isi sanad ke sath moquf riwayat kya hai."
1738,"Hazrat abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi aurat ko , jiska bacha gum jaey, tasalli deta hai to usey jannat main eik qeemti libas pehnaya jaeyga.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1739,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Jaafar ki shahadat ki khabar aai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aale-Jaafar ke liye khana tayyar karo, unke paas aisi chiz (yani khabar) aai hai jo unhen mashghool rakhegi.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
1740,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs par nauha kya jaey to is par nauha kiye janey ke baais roze-qiyamat usey azab diya jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
1741,"Hazrat Umra binte Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, aur unhen bataya gaya ke Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maiyat ko , uskey qabiley ke is par roney ki wajeh sey, azab diya jata hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah ! Abu-Abdur-Rehman ko maaf farmaai , unhoney jhoot nahin bola , balke wo bhool gaey ya ghalati kar gaey, baat sirf itni hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Yahudi aurat ke paas se guzrey jis par uskey ghar waley ro rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak ye to is par ro rahey hain jabkey usey apni qabr mein azab ho raha hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1742,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Muleka (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti Makka mein wafat pa gaeen to ham uskey janaze mein shareek honey ke liye aaye jabkey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi tashrif laye they, mein un dono ke darmiyan betha hua tha, Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Amr bin Usman se farmaya : jabkey wo uskey muqabil they, kya tum roney se mana nahin kartey? kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maiyat ko , uskey ghar walon ke is par roney ki wajeh sey, azab diya jata hai.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : umr (Raziallahu anhu) iska baaz hissey bayan kiya kartey they, phir unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne hadees bayan ki to farmaya : main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka se wapis aaya, yahan tak ke jab ham Beda ke qarib pahunchey to unhoney keekar ke saye taley eik qafila dekha to farmaya : jaao dekho ke ye kon log hain? maine dekha to wo Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) they, chunanche maine unko bataya , to unhoney farmaya is (Suhaib (Raziallahu anhu)) ko bulaao, main Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya to maine kaha : yahan se kooch karo aur ameerul-momeneen ke paas chalo , phir jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakhmi kar diya gaya, to Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) rotey huey aaye aur kehney lagey : aah bhai par kitna afsos hai ! aah bhai par kitna afsos hai ! to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Suheb ! kya tum mujh par rotey ho? jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maiyat ko uskey ghar walon ki taraf se is par roney ki wajeh se azab diya jata hai.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey to maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ye zikr kiya to unhoney farmaya : Allah umr (Raziallahu anhu) par rehem farmaey, nahin, Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye hadees bayan nahin ki ke ''maiyat ko uskey ghar walon ki taraf se is par roney ki wajeh se azab diya jata hai.'' balke ''Allah kafir shakhs par, uskey ghar walon ke roney ki wajeh se azab badha deta hai.'' aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : tumhen Quran kafi hona chahiye : ''koi bojh uthaney wali kisi dusri jaan ka bojh nahin uthaeygi.'' is par ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah hi hansata aur rulata hai. ibne-Abi Muleka ne farmaya : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne koi baat na ki. muttafaq aleh."
1743,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ibne-Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) , Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ki khabar shahadat pahunchi to aap ( masjid mein) beth gaey aur aap ke chehrey par gham ke aasaar wazeh they, aur main darwazey ki jhuri se dekh rahi thi, itney main eik aadmi aap ke paas aaya to usney arz kiya : Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khawatin ro rahi hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya ke : ''unhen mana karo.'' wo chala gaya (aur unhen mana kiya lekin wo baaz na aayen) phir wo dusri martaba aap ke paas aaya aur arz kiya ke wo uski baat nahin maantee , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen mana kar.'' lekin wo teesri martaba phir aaya aur arz kiya : Allah ki qism ! Allah ke Rasool ! wo ham par ghalib aa gaeen hain, (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu)) ne guman kiya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unke munh mein mitti dalo.'' maine kaha : Allah teri naak khaak aalud karey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo hukm diya to usey baja laya na Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko takleef pahunchana tarak kiya. muttafaq aleh."
1744,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey to maine kaha : pardesi shakhs pardes mein faut ho gaya, main is martaba is qadr roungi ke eik daastaan bin jaeygi, main is par roney ki puri tayyari kar chuki thi ke eik aurat aai wo roney mein mera sath dena chahti thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''kya tum aisey ghar mein shetan dakhil karna chahti ho jahan se Allah ne usey nikal bahar kya hai.'' aapney do martaba aisey farmaya. isliye main roney se ruk gaee aur main na roee. rawahu Muslim."
1745,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) par be-hoshi taari hui to unki behan Umra roney lagin aur kehney lagin , aah pahad par kitna afsos aah is tarah aur is tarah , wo unki khoobiyan bayan karney lagin, jab unhen hosh aaya to unhoney farmaya : aapney jo kuch bhi kaha, wo mujh se puchha gaya ke kya tum isi tarah ho? aur eik riwayat mein ye naqal kiya hai : jab wo (Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu)) Shaheed huey to phir wo un par na ro'ein. Bukhari."
1746,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab koi shakhs faut ho jata hai aur usey roney waley khadey ho kar kehtey hain : aah pahad ! aah sardar ! aur is tarah ki koi baat , to Allah us (maiyat) par do farishtey muqarrar farma deta hai jo usey maartay huey dhakkey de-kar kehtey hain : kya to aisey hi tha?'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1747,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aal mein se koi shakhs faut ho gaya, to aurten jama ho kar is par roney lagin , jabkey umr (Raziallahu anhu) unhen rokney aur door hataney ke liye khadey huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umar inhen chhod do, kyonkey aankh aansu hai aur dil ghamzada hai aur abhi sadma taza hai.''"
1748,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sahibzadi Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) wafat pa gaeen to khawatin roney lagin , to umr (Raziallahu anhu) kodey ke sath unhen maarney lagey jis par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney daste-mubarak ke sath unhen peechhey kar diya aur farmaya : ''Umar ! kuchh mohlat do.'' phir farmaya : ''(khawatin ki jamaat) shetani aawaz se bacho.'' phir farmaya : ''jahan tak aankh (aankh mein aansu honey) aur dil (ke ghamgin honey) ka talluq hai to wo Shan Wale Allah ki taraf se hai aur rehmat hai, aur jo haath aur zaban se koi harkat ho to wo shetan ki taraf se hai.''"
1749,"Hazrat Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne muallaq riwayat bayan ki hai ke jab Hasan bin Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey to unki ehliya ne saal bhar ke liye unki qabr par khema laga liya, phir unhoney utha liya to unhoney kisi pukarney waley ko suna : kya unhoney apni khoee hui chiz ko pa liya? doosrey ne jawab diya, nahin balke mayus ho gaey to wapis chaley gaey. Bukhari."
1750,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik janaazey mein shareek huey to aapney kuchh logon ko dekha ke unhoney apni ooper wali chadaren utaar phenki hain aur sirf qameez pehan kar chal rahey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (ye manzar dekh kar) farmaya : ''kya tum jahiliyat ka sa kaam kar rahey ho ya jahiliyat ke kaam se mushaabihat ikhtiyar kar rahey ho? maine irada kiya ke tumharey liye badduaa karun ke tumhari soorten maskh ho jaeyn.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, unhoney apni chadaren ley lein aur phir dobara aisey nahin kiya."
1751,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey janaazey mein shareek honey se mana farmaya jiskey sath koi nauha karney wali ho."
1752,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne un se kaha ke mera beta faut ho gaya to maine is par bahut gham kya, kya aapney apney khaleel (Salwatullah aleh) se koi aisi chiz suni hai jis se ham apney faut ho janey walon ke barey mein apney dilon ko khush kar lein? unhoney farmaya : haan maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' unke chhotey bachey jannat ke keedey hongey, un mein se eik apney walid se mulaqat kerega to wo usey kapdey ke kinarey se pakad lega , phir wo us se alag nahin hoga yahan tak ke wo usey jannat mein ley jaeyga.'' Muslim , Ahmed, aur alfaz musnad Ahmed ke hain. rawahu Muslim w Ahmed ."
1753,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! aap ki hadees ke mamley mein mard hazraat sabqat ley gaey, aap hamarey liye bhi eik din muqarrar farma den, jis roz ham aap ki khidmat mein hazir hun aap hamen wo taalim den jo Allah ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko di hai, aapney farmaya : '' aap falan falan din falan falan jagah jama ho jaya karen .'' pas wo ikhatti ho gaeen to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas tashrif laye to aapney Allah ki taalimaat mein se unhen kuch taalimaat din, phir farmaya : ''tum mein se jiskey teen bachey faut ho jaeyn to wo uskey liye jahannam se hijaab bin jaeyngey '' un mein se kisi aurat ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar do hun? usney do martaba ye baat kahi , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar do hon, agar do hon, agar do hon.'' Bukhari ."
1754,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis musalman waliden ke teen bachey faut ho jaeyn to Allah un par apna Fazal w karam farmatey huey unhen jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga .'' Sahaba ne arz kya : agar do hun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar do hon, unhoney phir arz kya, agar eik ho? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar eik ho tab bhi.'' phir farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism : jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! na-mukammal bacha apni maa ko apni naaf se khinch kar jannat mein ley jaeyga, b-sharte-ke wo us (ki wafat) par sabr karey.'' Ahmed, ibne-Maja ne (wallazi nafsi bi-yadi) se aakhir tak hadees riwayat ki hai."
1755,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke teen na-baligh bachchey faut ho jaeyn to wo uskey liye jahannam se mazbut hisar bin jaeyngey.'' Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : merey do bachchey faut huey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do bhi.'' Sayedul-Qurra Abu Munzir Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, mera eik bachcha faut hua hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik bhi.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1756,"Hazrat Qurrat Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi apney bete ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya karta tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''kya tum is se mohabbat kartey ho?'' usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main jaisey is se mohabbat karta hun wesay Allah aap se mohabbat karey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey na paya to puchha : '' ibne falan ko kya hua hai? '' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! wo faut ho gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum pasand nahin kartey ke tum jannat ke jis darwazey par jaao to tum usey wahan apna muntazir paao?'' kisi aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye us shakhs ke liye khas hai ya ham sab ke liye hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''balke tum sab ke liye hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
1757,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab na mukammal paida honey waley bachchey ke waliden ko jahannam mein dakhil kiye janey ka irada kiya jaeyga to wo apney rab se jhagda kerega, to usey kaha jaeyga : apney rab se jhagda karney waley na mukammal bachchey ! apney waliden ko jannat mein ley ja , wo apney aanwal se unhen kheencheyga yahan tak ke unhen jannat mein ley jaeyga.''"
1758,"Hazrat Abu Amaama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tabarak w taala farmata hai : ibne-Adam ! agar to ne sadmey ki ibtida (shuruat) par hi sabr kiya aur sawab ki ummid ki to main terey liye jannat se kam tar sawab par razi nahin hunga.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
1759,"Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi musalman mard ya musalman aurat kisi musibat mein mubtala ho jaey, aur phir us (musibat ke waqey honey) ke taweel muddat baad usey naey sirey se yad aa jaey aur wo (inna lillah w inna ilaihi raajioon) padh ley to Allah tabarak w taala usey naey sirey se itna hi sawab ata farma deta hai jitna usney us musibat ke waqey honey ke roz sawab ata kiya tha.''"
1760,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ke jootey ka tasma toot jaey to wo ( inna lillah w inna ilaihi raajioon ( padhey , kyonkey ye bhi masaayib mein se hai.''"
1761,"Hazrat Umme-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna, unhoney kaha : maine abul-Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah tabarak w taala ne farmaya : ''Esa! main terey baad eik ummat bhejney wala hun, jab unhen koi pasandida chiz milegi to wo Allah ki hamd bayan karengey, aur agar kisi nagawar chiz se wastey pad gaya to wo sawab ki ummid ke sath sabr karengey, halanke koi hilm w aql nahin hogi, unhoney arz kya : merey parwardigar! ye kaisey ho sakta hai jabkey hilm w aql na ho? farmaya : ''main unhen apney hilm w ilm se ata karunga.''"
1762,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen qabron ki ziyaarat se mana kya tha, ( ab ( unki ziyaarat kya karo, maine tumhen teen din se zayed qurbani ka gosht rakhney se mana kya tha, ab jis qadr zarurat mehsus karo usey rakho , maine mishkeezey ke ilawa nabeez bananey se tumhen mana kya tha, tum tamam bartanon mein nabeez bana saktey ho, lekin nasha aawar mashrub istimal na karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1763,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni walida ki qabr ki ziyaarat ki to aap khud bhi roey aur apney Aas paas walon ko bhi rulaaya, phir farmaya : ''maine unki maghfirat talab karney ke mutalliq apney rab se ijazat talab ki to mujhey uski ijazat na mili , phir maine unki qabr ki ziyaarat ke mutalliq us se ijazat talab ki to mujhey ijazat mil gaee , pas tum qabron ki ziyaarat kya karo, kyonkey wo maut yad dilati hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1764,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab wo qabristaan janey ka irada kartey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Alaihissalam) unhen ye dua sikhaya kartey they : ''momin aur musalman ghar walon par salamti ho, agar Allah ne chaha to ham tumharey sath milney waley hain, ham apney aur tumharey liye Allah se aafiyat talab kartey hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1765,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka Madina ki qabron ke paas se guzar hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki taraf chehra Mubarak kartey huey farmaya : '' ehle quboor ! tum par salamti ho, Allah hamen aur tumhen maaf farmaai , tum hamarey aslaaf ho aur ham tumharey peechey aaney waley hain.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1766,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka raat qiyam merey paas hota to aap raat ke aakhiri hissey mein baqee ( qabristaan ( ki taraf tashrif ley jatey aur farmatey : '' momin qom ke gharo ! tum par salamti ho aur jis kal ke liye tum se wada kya gaya tha aur tumhen uskey liye mohlat di gaee thi wo tum tak pahunch chuka , aur be-shak ham tum se milney waley hain, aey Allah ! baqee gharqad walon ki maghfirat farma .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1767,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ziyaarate-quboor ke moqe par mein kaisey dua karun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye dua karen : momin aur musalman ghar walon par salamti ho, Allah ham se aagey janey walon aur ham se peechey reh janey walon par rehem farmaai , aur agar Allah ne chaha to be-shak ham bhi tum se milney waley hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1768,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Noman , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfoo riwayat kartey hain aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs her Jumey apney waliden ya un mein se kisi eik ki qabr ki ziyaarat karta hai to usey bakhsh diya jata hai aur usey ( waliden ka ( itaat guzar likha jata hai.'' Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein mursal riwayat kya hai."
1769,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen qabron ki ziyaarat se mana kya karta tha, ab unki ziyaarat kya karo, kyonkey wo duniya se be raghbat karti hain aur aakhirat ki yad dilati hain.''"
1770,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kasrat ke sath qabron ki ziyaarat karney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai. Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. mazeed farmaya : baaz ehle ilm ka khayal hai ke ye ziyaarate-quboor ke mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki rukhsat se pehley tha, jab aapney ijazat de-di to aap ki ijazat mein mard aur aurten sab dakhil hain, aur un mein se baaz ne kaha : aapney aurton ke qabristaan janey ko isliye na pasand farmaya ke wo sabr kam karti hain, jabkey rona-dhona ziyada karti hain, Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ka kalam mukammal hua . rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
1771,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main apney us hujrey mein jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (madfun) hain chali jaya karti thi, aur yahin apni chadar utaar diya karti thi, aur main (dil mein) kehti thi : wo to merey shohar hain aur doosrey merey walid hain, jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko unke sath dafn kar diya gaya to Allah ki qism ! main umr (Raziallahu anhu) se haya ki wajeh se apney ooper achhi tarah chadar lekar wahan dakhil hoti hun.'' rawahu Ahmed."
